3},"action":"insert","lines":[" "],"id":290}],[{"start":{"row":132,"column":33},"end":{"row":132,"column":58},"action":"insert","lines":["id=\"circle-shape-example\""],"id":291}],[{"start":{"row":132,"column":58},"end":{"row":132,"column":65},"action":"insert","lines":["></div>"],"id":292}],[{"start":{"row":132,"column":65},"end":{"row":133,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""],"id":293},{"start":{"row":133,"column":0},"end":{"row":133,"column":28},"action":"insert","lines":["                            "]}],[{"start":{"row":133,"column":28},"end":{"row":133,"column":65},"action":"insert","lines":["<div id=\"circle-shape-example\"></div>"],"id":294}],[{"start":{"row":133,"column":65},"end":{"row":134,"column":0},"action":"insert","lines":["",""],"id":295},{"start":{"row":134,"column":0},"end":{"row":134,"column":28},"action":"insert","lines":["                            "]}],[{"start":{"row":134,"column":28},"end":{"row":134,"column":65},"action":"insert","lines":["<div id=\"circle-shape-example\"></div>"],"id":296}],[{"start":{"row":138,"column":28},"end":{"row":140,"column":32},"action":"remove","lines":["<p class=\"methodText\">","                                IaaS is one of the fundamental service models provided in Cloud Computing. In this model your entire IT infrastructure can be provided as a service through the cloud providers. It includes provisions such as virtual server space, network connections, load balancers and configurations. Enterprises can utilize this infrastructure and build their own platforms on top of it to drive growth in business value. The location of data centers, present around the globe, is abstracted from the organization and in turn provides enhanced security and scalability options for them. It is a cost effective and scalable way to reduce both your IT costs and burdens.","                            </p>"],"id":303}],[{"start":{"row":132,"column":59},"end":{"row":134,"column":28},"action":"insert","lines":["","                                ","                            "],"id":304}],[{"start":{"row":133,"column":32},"end":{"row":135,"column":32},"action":"insert","lines":["<p class=\"methodText\">","                                IaaS is one of the fundamental service models provided in Cloud Computing. In this model your entire IT infrastructure can be provided as a service through the cloud providers. It includes provisions such as virtual server space, network connections, load balancers and configurations. Enterprises can utilize this infrastructure and build their own platforms on top of it to drive growth in business value. The location of data centers, present around the globe, is abstracted from the organization and in turn provides enhanced security and scalability options for them. It is a cost effective and scalable way to reduce both your IT costs and burdens.","                            </p>"],"id":305}],[{"start":{"row":132,"column":59},"end":{"row":133,"column":32},"action":"insert","lines":["","                                "],"id":306}],[{"start":{"row":133,"column":32},"end":{"row":133,"column":146},"action":"insert","lines":[" <img src=\"../images/why/bigdata.png\" alt=\"Certified Professionals\" class=\"curve\"><h1>Certified Professionals</h1>"],"id":307}],[{"start":{"row":141,"column":40},"end":{"row":141,"column":74},"action":"remove","lines":["Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS)"],"id":308}],[{"start":{"row":133,"column":118},"end":{"row":133,"column":141},"action":"remove","lines":["Certified Professionals"],"id":309},{"start":{"row":133,"column":118},"end":{"row":133,"column":152},"action":"insert","lines":["Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS)"]}],[{"start":{"row":150,"column":27},"end":{"row":152,"column":32},"action":"remove","lines":[" <p class=\"methodText\">","                                The PaaS model allows users and developers to build application in the cloud. Your web browser can become an simple IDE, providing enhanced development platforms and extended services to enable your teams to build scalable high performance applications in the cloud. Deployment and Maintenance of the applications can also be done through your web console provided by the PaaS provider. Databases, Pre-Built Services, 3rd Party API’s and many more features make this model both lucrative and beneficial for the enterprise. No investment for infrastructure, and a pay-as-you-use model helps to drastically reduce and optimize your IT costs. This model also helps to reduce the time-to-market of a product by helping different teams collaborate from varied physical locations.","                            </p>"],"id":313}],[{"start":{"row":138,"column":59},"end":{"row":140,"column":28},"action":"insert","lines":["","                                ","                            "],"id":314}],[{"start":{"row":139,"column":32},"end":{"row":141,"column":32},"action":"insert","lines":[" <p class=\"methodText\">","                                The PaaS model allows users and developers to build application in the cloud. Your web browser can become an simple IDE, providing enhanced development platforms and extended services to enable your teams to build scalable high performance applications in the cloud. Deployment and Maintenance of the applications can also be done through your web console provided by the PaaS provider. Databases, Pre-Built Services, 3rd Party API’s and many more features make this model both lucrative and beneficial for the enterprise. No investment for infrastructure, and a pay-as-you-use model helps to drastically reduce and optimize your IT costs. This model also helps to reduce the time-to-market of a product by helping different teams collaborate from varied physical locations.","                            </p>"],"id":315}],[{"start":{"row":138,"column":59},"end":{"row":139,"column":32},"action":"insert","lines":["","                                "],"id":318}],[{"start":{"row":139,"column":32},"end":{"row":139,"column":157},"action":"insert","lines":[" <img src=\"../images/why/bigdata.png\" alt=\"Certified Professionals\" class=\"curve\"><h1>Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS)</h1>"],"id":319}],[{"start":{"row":153,"column":40},"end":{"row":153,"column":68},"action":"remove","lines":["Platform as a Service (PaaS)"],"id":320}],[{"start":{"row":139,"column":118},"end":{"row":139,"column":152},"action":"remove","lines":["Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS)"],"id":321},{"start":{"row":139,"column":118},"end":{"row":139,"column":146},"action":"insert","lines":["Platform as a Service (PaaS)"]}],[{"start":{"row":145,"column":27},"end":{"row":155,"column":27},"action":"remove","lines":[" <p class=\"methodText\">","                                <strong></strong>","                            </p>","                            ","                           ","                           ","","                            <p class=\"methodText\">","                                <strong></strong>","                            </p>","                           "],"id":322}],[{"start":{"row":149,"column":26},"end":{"row":151,"column":36},"action":"remove","lines":["  <p class=\"methodText\">","                                SaaS, by concept, is defined as any cloud service where the consumers can access software applications hosted in the cloud. Users can access these applications through a multitude of devices, over the internet. Unlike the regular purchase-and-install model, applications in the cloud work on a subscription based model. Automatic updates in the cloud, personalized directories and anywhere accesses are some of the basic features that drive this model. Usage is scalable and increased needs can be addressed with a single-click. Software in the cloud is not only easily scalable, but it is also customizable to ensure that it fits the enterprises brand and needs.","                            </p><br>"],"id":323}],[{"start":{"row":144,"column":59},"end":{"row":146,"column":28},"action":"insert","lines":["","                                ","                            "],"id":324}],[{"start":{"row":145,"column":32},"end":{"row":147,"column":36},"action":"insert","lines":["  <p class=\"methodText\">","                                SaaS, by concept, is defined as any cloud service where the consumers can access software applications hosted in the cloud. Users can access these applications through a multitude of devices, over the internet. Unlike the regular purchase-and-install model, applications in the cloud work on a subscription based model. Automatic updates in the cloud, personalized directories and anywhere accesses are some of the basic features that drive this model. Usage is scalable and increased needs can be addressed with a single-click. Software in the cloud is not only easily scalable, but it is also customizable to ensure that it fits the enterprises brand and needs.","                            </p><br>"],"id":325}],[{"start":{"row":144,"column":59},"end":{"row":145,"column":32},"action":"insert","lines":["","                                "],"id":326}],[{"start":{"row":145,"column":32},"end":{"row":145,"column":151},"action":"insert","lines":[" <img src=\"../images/why/bigdata.png\" alt=\"Certified Professionals\" class=\"curve\"><h1>Platform as a Service (PaaS)</h1>"],"id":327}],[{"start":{"row":152,"column":40},"end":{"row":152,"column":68},"action":"remove","lines":["Software as a Service (SaaS)"],"id":328}],[{"start":{"row":145,"column":118},"end":{"row":145,"column":146},"action":"remove","lines":["Platform as a Service (PaaS)"],"id":329},{"start":{"row":145,"column":118},"end":{"row":145,"column":146},"action":"insert","lines":["Software as a Service (SaaS)"]}],[{"start":{"row":151,"column":26},"end":{"row":154,"column":26},"action":"remove","lines":["  <p class=\"methodText\">","                                <strong></strong>","                            </p>","                          "],"id":33